{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 74089, "create_time": 1649866025, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "真要共存了，他们会觉得是政府抛弃他们了...", "timestamp": 1649866025}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 74161, "create_time": 1649869929, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "这两年政府也没说向大众灌输逐渐开放的思想啊，，这局面还不是他们自己造成的. ", "timestamp": 1649869929}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 74162, "create_time": 1649870020, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "有时候我真搞不清楚他们到底在不在意民众的支持. 说他们在意吧，他们又挺鱼肉百姓的; 说他们不在意吧，该决断的时候又考虑起广大清零派了..", "timestamp": 1649870020}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 74185, "create_time": 1649874830, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "不用怀疑，中国大多数人就是清零，怕病毒怕得要死的那种。中国政府这两年的宣传，包括现在，都是把病毒宣扬到极度危险，来宣扬自己防疫的“成就”", "timestamp": 1649874830}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 74186, "create_time": 1649875008, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "但他们的生活和19年之前相同就大错特错了。疫情的防控政策下，基层的普通商户、小工厂根本扛不住，打工的也分分钟可能被灵活就业。而且要是运气不好碰到武汉上海封城，是真的悲惨", "timestamp": 1649875008}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 74215, "create_time": 1649892376, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Carol: 大量县城2020年春节后就没有封过城了", "timestamp": 1649892376}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 74231, "create_time": 1649896720, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Dave: 然而现在是2022年Omicron BA.2的时代，现在是轮流封城，打开搜索引擎随便搜搜，就现在，公交停运的小县城多得是", "timestamp": 1649896720}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 74247, "create_time": 1649898607, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Dave: 这话放在去年对，但现在某个地级市出一个病例，下辖所有县全部停摆，越小的地方封的越严", "timestamp": 1649898607}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 74366, "create_time": 1649905526, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "不管是不是鱼肉，总之在做事就对了；对于大部分人来讲，政府不做事才是会被批评的。", "timestamp": 1649905526}], "create_time": 1649865845, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1649905526, "likenum": 11, "n_attentions": 11, "n_comments": 9, "pid": 27303, "poll": null, "reply": 9, "text": "按人头算，中国支持清零的说不定真占多数\n一线城市承担着最大的疫情爆发风险，经历着最频繁的疫情防控\n但还有多少中小城市、农村地区，从20年起也就那么一两次疫情甚至没有疫情，很多人连县都不怎么出\n他们现在的生活，和19年没有太大区别，他们切实享受着封控的好处，你想拖他们去共存谈何容易", "timestamp": 1649865845}}